data.description: Investors are sure to be intrigued by the expansive ranch situated on over half an acre of land. The property comes complete with a spacious garage, recently updated siding, a fenced yard, and both well and septic systems. While these features are in place, some updates may be needed.    Originally a duplex, the property has been cleverly converted into a single-family home with three bedrooms and two full baths. This unique history adds a touch of character to the property.    In summary, this ranch offers investors a promising opportunity with its spacious land, functional features, and potential for updates. Its  a property worth considering for those looking to invest.
